    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Vodafone Idea Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Backend Developer to strengthen our Pimpri-Chinchwad-based team.\n\nAbout Vodafone Idea Holdings Services:\nVodafone Idea Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Vodafone Idea Holdings Services!",
